'''后髮座星系團''' （[[阿貝爾星系團表|阿貝爾]]1656）是一個巨大的[[星系團|星系團]]，擁有1,000個以上被確認的星系<ref name="chandra"/><ref name="nasafocuscoma"/>。一起的[[獅子座星系團|獅子座星系團]]（阿貝爾1367），都是[[后髮座超星系團|后髮座超星系團]]的兩個主要成員<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Coma Supercluster|url=http://www.atlasoftheuniverse.com/superc/com.html|accessdate=2008-03-30|archive-date=2009-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090129203005/http://atlasoftheuniverse.com/superc/com.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它位於[[后髮座|后髮座]]內，因此以該星座的名稱命名。

這個星系團與地球的平均距離是9,900萬[[秒差距|秒差距]]（3億2100萬[[光年|光年]]）<ref name="nasafocuscoma"/><ref name="IPAC">{{cite web |title=2MASS Atlas Image Gallery: Galaxy Groups and Clusters |publisher=Infrared Processing and Analysis Center |url=http://www.ipac.caltech.edu/2mass/gallery/images_galcl.html |accessdate=2010-05-02 |archive-date=2018-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180114005036/https://www.ipac.caltech.edu/2mass/gallery/images_galcl.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite encyclopedia | last = Colless | first = M | editor = P Murdin | encyclopedia = Encyclopedia of Astronomy and Astrophysics | title = Coma Cluster | url = http://eaa.iop.org/abstract/0333750888/2600 | accessdate = 2006-10-08 | year = 2001 | publisher = Bristol Institute of Physics publishing | archive-date = 2014-10-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141028230004/http://eaa.crcpress.com/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，其中最亮的10個[[螺旋星系|螺旋星系]]的[[視星等|視星等]]在12至14等之間，業餘天文學家使用口徑20公分以上的望遠鏡就能看見{{Citation needed|date=February 2007}}。在中間主宰著星系團的是兩個巨大的[[橢圓星系|橢圓星系]]： [[NGC_4874|NGC 4874]]和[[NGC_4889|NGC 4889]]<ref>{{cite journal | author = Conselice, Christopher J., Gallagher, John S., III | title = Galaxy aggregates in the Coma cluster | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | year = 1998 | volume = 297 | issue = 2 | pages = L34–L38 | url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/bib_query?astro-ph/9801160 | doi = 10.1046/j.1365-8711.1998.01717.x|arxiv = astro-ph/9801160 |bibcode = 1998MNRAS.297L..34C }}</ref>。這個星系團離天球上的[[銀河|銀河]]北極點只有幾度。在后髮座星系團中心部分的星系大多是巨大的橢圓星系，而在這個星系團中有著豐富的矮星系和巨大的橢圓星系<ref>[http://newswise.com/articles/view/541574/ Newswise: Hubble's Sweeping View of the Coma Cluster of Galaxies] {{Wayback|url=http://newswise.com/articles/view/541574/ |date=20160918053118 }} Retrieved on June 11, 2008.</ref>。

== 星系間的氣體 ==
這個集團的星系都被非常高溫的[[星系間物質|星系間氣體]]籠罩著，並輻射出值得注意的[[X-射線|X-射線輻射]]{{Fact|time=2007-07-16T11:04:47Z}}。這些游離的氣體也改變了[[宇宙微波背景輻射|宇宙微波背景輻射]]的[[微波|微波]][[光譜|光譜]]，這種效應稱為[[Sunyaev-Zel'dovich效應|Sunyaev-Zel'dovich效應]]<ref name="depetrisetal2002">{{cite journal
  | author=M. De Petris, L. D'Alba, L. Lamagna, F. Melchiorri, A. Orlando, E. Palladino, Y. Rephaeli, S. Colafrancesco, E. Kreysa, M. Signore
  | title=MITO Measurements of the Sunyaev-Zeldovich Effect in the Coma Cluster of Galaxies
  | journal=Astrophysical Journal
  | year=2002
  | volume=574
  | pages=L119-L122
  | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2002ApJ...574L.119D
  | access-date=2007-01-10
  | archive-date=2007-03-27
  | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070327154801/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2002ApJ...574L.119D
  | dead-url=no
  }}</ref>。這些星系間的氣體質量遠大於這個星系集團中星系的總質量。{{Fact|time=2007-07-16T11:04:47Z}}

